OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHead teachers 'pushed to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fedge of despair'           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, School leaders are being "pushed to the
OL,6, edge of despair" by inspections and    
OL,7, workload, a union has said.            
OL,9,FThe National Association of Head       
OL,10,FTeachers (NAHT) warned of a mass exodus
OL,11,Ffrom top school jobs without reforms.  
OL,13,FIt says a snapshot of school leaders'  
OL,14,Fviews found almost half needed support 
OL,15,Ffor their mental health or wellbeing in
OL,16,Fthe last year.                         
OL,18,FIt comes after an inquest found an     
OL,19,FOfsted inspection contributed to head  
OL,20,Fteacher Ruth Perry taking her own life.
